events.text: The boy swung the axe to his sisterâ€™s neck. As her blood splashes onto the floor, the six candles burned down.
It was over. The old lady was nowhere to be found, and what was his sister lies on the floor.
The boy absent-mindedly walked away, not knowing the path to his home. As the boy grew hungrier, the night grew more and more darker.
As the boy finally collapses, he sees the silhouette of his sister for the last time.
